This package was extracted and generalized from the mindXtrain project
(https://github.com/Professor-Codephreak/mindXtrain), specifically the
`mindxtrain/autotune/` package and the consumer-side helpers in
`mindxtrain/train/sft.py` and `mindxtrain/train/axolotl_compile.py`. The
original was MI300X / ROCm `gfx942`-only; this version carries a
HardwareProfile and supports AMD/ROCm, NVIDIA/CUDA, and CPU.
